<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="SB0209" sponsor="Derrin R. Owens" designation="SB" otherSponsor="" otherHouse="House" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL0907" date="1/28/2026 08:01:357" printDate="01-28 08:15" subVer="0" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>3</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="05/06/2026"><seclist><sect action="E" src="code" buid="1" uid="C79-4-S609_2026050620260506" sort="79 04 06090020260506" mtype="section" effdate="05/06/2026">79-4-609</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="2" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="05/06/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Gooseberry Narrows State Park Designation</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Derrin R. Owens</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>House Sponsor: </otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill addresses the creation of Gooseberry Narrows State Park.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">authorizes the Division of State Parks (division) to:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="2">enter into an agreement with the United States Forest Service (USFS) to operate land <ln numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10"/>managed by USFS as a state park;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11" level="2">receive donations of land or facilities in the gooseberry narrows; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="12" slineno="0-12" level="2">engage in transfers, exchanges, or purchases of land in the gooseberry narrows;</hl></hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13" level="1">allows the division to consult with local governments regarding:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="14" slineno="0-14" level="2">the construction of a dam at Gooseberry Narrows State Park;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="15" slineno="0-15" level="2">the necessary acquisition or transfer of water rights for a potential dam at Gooseberry <ln numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16"/>Narrows State Park; and </hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="17" slineno="0-17" level="2">resolving disputes related to the development of Gooseberry Narrows State Park; and</hl></hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18" level="1">provides that Gooseberry Narrows State Park is part of the state park system upon the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19"/>division entering into an agreement with USFS.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="0-20" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="21">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="0-22">Other Special Clauses:</oc><ocNone lineno="23">None</ocNone><sa numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="0-24">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saent numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="0-25"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="79-4-609" src="code" uid="C79-4-S609_2026050620260506" buid="1" sort="79 04 06090020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="0-26"><bold>79-4-609</bold>, Utah Code Annotated 1953</sn></saent></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="27"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="0-28">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="1" num="79-4-609" type="enact" src="code" uid="C79-4-S609_2026050620260506" sort="79 04 06090020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-2" number="79-4-609" type="enact"><secline lineno="29">Section 1. Section <bold>79-4-609</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><catline lineno="30"><bold>79-4-609<parens/>. Gooseberry Narrows State Park.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="1-1" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-3" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1000" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="11" groupid="8" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">As used in this section:</amend><subsection ssid="1-14" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-4" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="67" groupid="49" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"Gooseberry narrows" means the land on Gooseberry Creek between the Lower <ln numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-5"/>Gooseberry Dam and Fairview Lakes described by the map and legal description on <ln numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-6"/>file with the division.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-15" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-7" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="68" groupid="50" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"Impacted local government" means a local government, as that term is defined in <ln numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-8"/>Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="63G-16-201">63G-16-201</xref>, that:</amend><subsection ssid="1-20" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-9" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="108" groupid="72" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">has jurisdictional land located within the gooseberry narrows;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-21" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-10" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="114" groupid="77" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">has a property interest in the gooseberry narrows;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-23" dnum="_-o:iii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-11" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="126" groupid="85" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">holds a water right or interest in a water right in Gooseberry Creek; or</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-22" dnum="_-o:iv-i" numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-12" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iv)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="121" groupid="81" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">manages land located within the gooseberry narrows.</amend></subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-2" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="1-13" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1007" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="8" groupid="6" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The division may enter into an agreement with the United States Forest Service to:</amend><subsection ssid="1-3" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="42" slineno="1-14" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1008" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="16" groupid="11" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">manage land in the gooseberry narrows;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-5" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="43" slineno="1-15" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1009" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="26" groupid="19" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">purchase or exchange land in the gooseberry narrows; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-4" dnum="_-o:c-i" numlevel="1" lineno="44" slineno="1-16" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1010" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(c)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="21" groupid="15" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">operate the gooseberry narrows as a state park.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-16" dnum="_-o:3-i" numlevel="1" lineno="45" slineno="1-17" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1011" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(3)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="72" groupid="53" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The division may consult with an impacted local government to:</amend><subsection ssid="1-17" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="46" slineno="1-18" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1012" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="83" groupid="58" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">in coordination with the Division of Water Resources created in Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="73-10-18">73-10-18</xref>, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="47" slineno="1-19"/>provide assistance on the development or construction of a dam at Gooseberry <ln numlevel="1" lineno="48" slineno="1-20"/>Narrows State Park;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-18" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="49" slineno="1-21" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1013" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="89" groupid="63" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">in coordination with the Division of Water Rights created in Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="73-2-1.1">73-2-1.1</xref>, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="50" slineno="1-22"/>provide information on the acquisition or transfer of a water right needed for the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="51" slineno="1-23"/>development of a dam at Gooseberry Narrows State Park; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-19" dnum="_-o:c-i" numlevel="1" lineno="52" slineno="1-24" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1014" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(c)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="99" groupid="68" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">resolve a dispute regarding the development of a dam at the Gooseberry Narrows <ln numlevel="1" lineno="53" slineno="1-25"/>State Park between:</amend><subsection ssid="1-24" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="54" slineno="1-26" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1015" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="131" groupid="89" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">two or more landowners;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-25" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="55" slineno="1-27" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1016" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="136" groupid="93" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a landowner and an impacted local government; or</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-26" dnum="_-o:iii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="56" slineno="1-28" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1017" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="141" groupid="97" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">two or more impacted local governments.</amend></subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-6" dnum="_-o:4-i" numlevel="1" lineno="57" slineno="1-29" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1018" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(4)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="27" groupid="20" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">If the division enters into an agreement as described in Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="79-4-609(2)">(2)</xref>, the gooseberry <ln numlevel="1" lineno="58" slineno="1-30"/>narrows is:</amend><subsection ssid="1-7" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="59" slineno="1-31" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1019" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="34" groupid="25" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">designated as Gooseberry Narrows State Park; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-8" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="60" slineno="1-32" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1020" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="39" groupid="29" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">included in the state park system.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-9" dnum="_-o:5-i" numlevel="1" lineno="61" slineno="1-33" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1021" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(5)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="40" groupid="30" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The division may:</amend><subsection ssid="1-10" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="62" slineno="1-34" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1022" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="47" groupid="35" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">receive donations of land or facilities in the gooseberry narrows for the creation of, <ln numlevel="1" lineno="63" slineno="1-35"/>and inclusion within, Gooseberry Narrows State Park;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-11" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="64" slineno="1-36" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1023" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="52" groupid="39" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">engage in land transfers and exchanges of land in the gooseberry narrows for <ln numlevel="1" lineno="65" slineno="1-37"/>inclusion in Gooseberry Narrows State Park; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="1-12" dnum="_-o:c-i" numlevel="1" lineno="66" slineno="1-38" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1024" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(c)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="57" groupid="43" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">purchase land or facilities in the gooseberry narrows for inclusion in Gooseberry <ln numlevel="1" lineno="67" slineno="1-39"/>Narrows State Park.</amend></subsection></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="2" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="68" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="68">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="69"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="5/6/2026">May 6, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>1-28-26 8:15 AM</tm></rev></foot></leg>